I don't think I have saved the source to Term::PfmColor anywhere.
You can circumvent it by adding the following lines at the top of
pfm.pl:

##################################################################

package Term::PfmColor;

require Term::ScreenColor;

@ISA = 'Term::ScreenColor';

sub new {
    my $self = shift;
    return $self->SUPER::new(@_);
}

package main;

